05:07.933 --> 05:12.436
<i> [sweeping instrumentals]</i>

05:13.314 --> 05:15.731
- Good afternoon.
I'm here to talk to the senator

05:15.816 --> 05:17.107
About boom regul--

05:17.526 --> 05:19.559
[rapidly] good afternoon,
I'm here to talk about--

05:19.570 --> 05:22.154
<i> [energetic music]</i>

05:22.197 --> 05:24.656
Ohh...Who would have thought

05:24.700 --> 05:25.866
It'd be so hard

05:25.951 --> 05:28.577
To get something done
in washington?

05:28.620 --> 05:31.496
<i> [downbeat bluesy music]</i>

05:31.582 --> 05:34.082
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

05:34.168 --> 05:35.751
- You want a belly rub?

05:35.794 --> 05:38.211
- Oh, no thank you,
sex hamster.

05:38.297 --> 05:42.090
But I totally respect
your gross profession.

05:42.801 --> 05:43.800
[phone rings]

05:43.886 --> 05:46.636
A phone?
Trapped in a glass box?

05:46.722 --> 05:48.305
I'll help you, phone!

05:48.390 --> 05:49.348
Hello?

05:49.433 --> 05:51.350
Aah!

05:55.064 --> 05:58.690
- Hello, @mrfloofypants.

05:58.776 --> 06:00.067
- How do you know my handle?

06:00.194 --> 06:01.985
- Everyone's talking about
the dog

06:02.071 --> 06:04.321
Who's got the balls
to go up against big boom.

06:04.406 --> 06:06.740
- They can't mean me.
I don't have any--

06:06.825 --> 06:08.408
Balls!
[laughing]

06:08.494 --> 06:12.204
I have balls!
Normally, I don't have those.

06:12.289 --> 06:14.915
- You're dreaming big, kid,
but you're on the wrong side.

06:14.958 --> 06:17.084
Big boom could use a dog
like you.

06:17.127 --> 06:18.960
So I'm gonna write down
an offer...

06:19.046 --> 06:20.670
- There's no amount of--

06:20.798 --> 06:22.172
Wow. That is a lotta bacon.

06:22.257 --> 06:24.925
- Chiefy, even with those
white-hot dream balls,

06:24.968 --> 06:27.010
Big boom
is too powerful to fight.

06:27.096 --> 06:29.471
Everything relies on
big boom--

06:29.556 --> 06:30.472
Agriculture,

06:30.599 --> 06:31.640
Military,

06:31.683 --> 06:33.892
The vengaboys.
- Oh, yeah?

06:33.936 --> 06:35.852
Lemme ask<i> you</i> something.

06:35.896 --> 06:37.771
Is that one cat?

06:37.815 --> 06:39.147
- Yes.
- Yes.

06:39.233 --> 06:41.733
- Oh, cool.
Lemme ask you something else.

06:41.777 --> 06:45.278
Why is a raccoon like you
on the side of big boom?

06:45.322 --> 06:46.905
Don't you get scared too?

06:46.990 --> 06:49.658
