of your uneaten children?

06:49.701 --> 06:53.328
- Sure, but we hide down here,
and if the booms get too loud,

06:53.414 --> 06:55.038
We'll just move to new zooland

06:55.082 --> 06:57.707
With the money we made
off big boom.

06:57.835 --> 06:59.668
And now you're probably
gonna ask,

06:59.795 --> 07:01.545
"ooh, what about the animals

07:01.588 --> 07:03.797
"who can't afford
underground hideouts

07:03.882 --> 07:05.882
"or land in new zooland?

07:05.926 --> 07:08.760
Waah!"
- I was gonna ask that.

07:08.846 --> 07:10.679
- Well, we don't worry
about them,

07:10.764 --> 07:12.139
Because they're not our base.

07:12.182 --> 07:14.558
- I'm gonna tell
senator mcturtle about this.

07:14.643 --> 07:17.978
- Ha, please. I've got
senator mcturtle in my pocket.

07:18.021 --> 07:21.189
- Chiefy!
Room in here for one more.

07:21.275 --> 07:23.942
- Senator mcturtle?
- That's right, chief.

07:24.027 --> 07:25.986
This fight goes all the way
to the top.

07:26.113 --> 07:27.863
- Top of what?
- The top of the tippy.

07:27.906 --> 07:29.114
- The tippy top?

07:29.199 --> 07:31.116
- Monkey!
Show this dumb dog out.

07:31.201 --> 07:32.576
- You don't scare me.

07:32.661 --> 07:35.662
All you've done is make me
more determined than ever--

07:35.747 --> 07:37.831
How are your hands so soft?

07:37.916 --> 07:40.625
<i> [dreamy chords]</i>

07:40.711 --> 07:41.960
<i> [upbeat music]</i>

07:42.045 --> 07:43.503
- Even though
it's a convertible,

07:43.589 --> 07:44.838
It's more fun like this.

07:44.923 --> 07:47.007
- Uh, honey,
I have a problem.

07:47.092 --> 07:49.259
- Nuh-uh.
We agreed: No problems.

07:49.303 --> 07:51.386
- I have to pee,
but if you don't wanna stop,

07:51.472 --> 07:53.763
I can just hold it in until
it comes out of my eyes

07:53.807 --> 07:55.557
Like tears.
- [groans]

07:55.642 --> 07:58.477
<i> [light rock music]</i>

07:58.562 --> 08:02.856
