08:02.900 --> 08:04.357
[urine splashing]

08:04.401 --> 08:07.819
- Well, well, well.
What do we have here?

08:07.905 --> 08:09.362
Yeah, it's me--max the pig

08:09.406 --> 08:11.406
As the police officer
in your dream.

08:11.533 --> 08:13.283
I expected better
from you, honey.

08:13.285 --> 08:15.035
- Sorry.
If you're not comfortable,

08:15.078 --> 08:16.661
I can try again.
- Nah, it's fine.

08:16.747 --> 08:17.913
I'm here.
Let's do this.

08:17.998 --> 08:20.790
Where you two city sniffers
headed?

08:20.876 --> 08:22.334
- Oh, we're just going
to relaxicon

08:22.419 --> 08:24.419
To escape the booms
and annoying problems.

08:24.505 --> 08:26.338
Like the one
we're dealing with now.

08:26.465 --> 08:28.673
- Now, public pee-pee
is against the law

08:28.759 --> 08:30.050
In these parts, ladies.

08:30.135 --> 08:32.969
I'm gonna have to give you
a urination citation.

08:32.971 --> 08:34.846
- [growls]
well, I'm gonna have to--

08:34.932 --> 08:36.348
- Oh--aah!
- Elsa!

08:36.391 --> 08:38.266
- That escalated quickly!

08:38.310 --> 08:40.268
- Oh, my god, oh, my god.
[cop yelling in background]

08:40.354 --> 08:41.436
- Drive!

08:43.524 --> 08:45.190
[siren wailing]

08:45.275 --> 08:47.776
- You bit a cop!
What were you thinking?

08:47.861 --> 08:49.319
- I killed a beaver in memphis.

08:49.363 --> 08:50.529
Drive!
- What?

08:50.572 --> 08:53.114
All I wanted to do was
get away from the booms

08:53.158 --> 08:55.242
At relaxicon,
and now we're fugitives,

08:55.285 --> 08:58.119
Which is kind of exciting,
but really annoying.

08:58.163 --> 09:01.122
I wish I was on this trip
with someone else!

09:01.166 --> 09:02.249
- Aah--
- what?

09:02.334 --> 09:03.291
Oh, hi, tabitha.

09:03.377 --> 09:05.585
- We are target
of police pursuit?

09:05.712 --> 09:07.462
You do pedals, I steer.

09:07.548 --> 09:09.548
- Aah!

09:13.762 --> 09:15.470
- [gasps]
son of a me!

09:15.514 --> 09:17.639
He's gaining on us.

09:17.724 --> 09:19.349
- Moscow drift--now!

09:23.564 --> 09:24.604
- Ah...Oh--

09:24.648 --> 09:27.232
Aah!

09:30.237 --> 09:33.238
- You're welcome.
- Relaxicon, here we come.

09:33.282 --> 09:35.031
- Ow! My gun's loose!
[gunshot]

09:35.117 --> 09:36.449
Missed me! Ha ha ha ha--

09:36.493 --> 09:37.492
[gunshot]
ow!

09:38.704 --> 09:41.913
<i> [rock music]</i>

09:41.999 --> 09:47.377
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

09:47.462 --> 09:50.297
- This is a protest
against big boom

09:50.424 --> 09:53.133
And its hold
on the american animal!

09:53.218 --> 09:57.220
We will no longer
hide under beds or take meds.

09:57.306 --> 09:59.639
All: [chanting]
no beds, no meds!

09:59.725 --> 10:01.099
No beds, no meds!

10:01.184 --> 10:04.060
- Oh, my god,
I'm being the change,

10:04.146 --> 10:05.687
And it's making me
more attractive.

10:05.772 --> 10:09.107
Which is not why I got into
this, but, you know...

10:09.192 --> 10:11.401
- Oh, my god!
- They won't silence us!

10:11.486 --> 10:13.903
- We gotta get outta here!
- Holy howl, the po-po's here!

10:13.989 --> 10:16.197
- Okay, disband immediately.

10:16.283 --> 10:18.158
You don't have permits
to protest here,

10:18.201 --> 10:20.952
And you're off leash.
- Yeah. What he said.

10:21.038 --> 10:23.371
- We have the right to
assemble, I read somewhere.

10:23.498 --> 10:26.416
- [neighing] noooo, not if
you're endangering the public.

10:26.501 --> 10:30.754
- Come on, man, we're all high
on cbd joint supplements.

10:30.797 --> 10:32.839
This is a peaceful protest.

10:32.924 --> 10:34.257
- Not anymore.

10:34.343 --> 10:37.552
[laughter]

10:40.140 --> 10:41.431
<i> [dramatic musical sting]</i>

10:41.475 --> 10:44.893
- They shut down our protest
and left us no choice.

10:44.936 --> 10:48.897
So welcome to the boom offense
organizing movement.

10:48.982 --> 10:50.273
Or...Boom.
- Meow!

10:50.317 --> 10:52.525
Sorry.
I'm afraid of acronyms.

10:52.611 --> 10:54.152
- This is our last chance

10:54.237 --> 10:56.655
To memorize the map
of the boom factory

10:56.740 --> 10:58.490
And its access points--

10:58.575 --> 11:00.909
Here, here, here, here,

11:00.952 --> 11:02.869
Here, here, here,

11:02.913 --> 11:05.705
Here, here, here, here.

11:05.791 --> 11:07.040
There's a lotta access.

11:07.125 --> 11:10.085
- If anyone's gettin'
cold paws, listen to this.

11:10.170 --> 11:12.545
Mrs. Mcturtle, tell our friends
what the senator let slip

11:12.631 --> 11:13.963
In the throes of passion.

11:14.049 --> 11:15.882
- The part about him
needing to be punished

11:15.967 --> 11:17.884
And how he wanted me
to stand on his--

11:17.928 --> 11:20.512
- Duh-ehh! No!
About the booms.

11:20.555 --> 11:22.847
- Oh. Well, they've known
about the devastating harm

11:22.933 --> 11:24.724
That booms cause to animals

11:24.768 --> 11:26.267
But hid the research.

11:26.311 --> 11:28.353
[all gasp]
- thank you, darla.

11:28.397 --> 11:29.813
We know how hard it must be

11:29.856 --> 11:31.189
To put your loyalty
to the cause

11:31.233 --> 11:33.024
Above your relationship
with the senator.

11:33.110 --> 11:34.734
- Oh, it's not that hard.

11:34.820 --> 11:36.277
- So we all know
what this means.

11:36.363 --> 11:40.532
- When facing injustice,
there is no choice but to act.

11:40.617 --> 11:42.659
I'm razzle dazzle!

11:42.786 --> 11:46.413
- It's time to give them
a taste of their own booms!

11:46.498 --> 11:49.082
- And that's when you said,
"it's time to give them

11:49.167 --> 11:51.543
A taste of their own booms."

11:51.628 --> 11:53.920
Isn't that correct, chief?

11:54.005 --> 11:55.880
- This is bullcrap, man!

11:55.966 --> 11:57.382
We all know
what's goin' on here.

11:57.467 --> 11:59.592
You're just using us
to distract from the bigger--

11:59.678 --> 12:02.679
- Bailiff, please shake a can
of pennies at the defendant.

12:02.723 --> 12:03.972
[rattling]
- ah!

12:04.015 --> 12:06.975
- You trespassed
on private property.

12:07.060 --> 12:09.102
<i> [suspenseful music]</i>

12:09.187 --> 12:11.980
<i> But before you could carry out</i>
<i> your dastardly assault,</i>

12:12.065 --> 12:15.734
<i> You were distracted</i>
<i> by the frpb.</i>

12:15.819 --> 12:18.153
The federal reserve
of peanut butter

